{"tid":1232837,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"好驚佔中2.0","createTime":"2019-06-16T16:35:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T23:52:48.000Z","uid":120772,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e5ab31764f4cebe6068d616603b1e2f8eb99187f","tid":1232837,"uid":120772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T16:35:11.000Z","msg":"其實可以學法國黃背心咁玩到個政府疲勞<br />\n真係要汲取上次教訓 唔好俾到藉口廢老藍絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b45065b3d663e102e9616df9247f360319ae8be","tid":1232837,"uid":53466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T23:51:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5d6773d2ad45272257d881dd5badda68bb506331","tid":1232837,"uid":93479,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T23:51:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我哋係要拎返香港，唔係拎條馬路呀</span>"},{"pid":"f3b320ab721a7f0202a43b3a408b4967a541d9f2","tid":1232837,"uid":93479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T23:52:48.000Z","msg":"法國黃背心運動的 8 堂課<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cup.com.hk/2019/06/14/lessons-from-the-yellow-vests/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cup.com.hk%2F2019%2F06%2F14%2Flessons-from-the-yellow-vests%2F&d=xNvf4PJMmDX7L7bksShbPocyEe9XGSmm9RGcz8BbYLg%3D&h=91a03058\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cup.com.hk/2019/06/14/lessons-from-the-yellow-vests/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2. 不死守任何公共空間<br />\n近年全球各地都流行佔領公共空間運動，縱然有助團結抗爭者，令其有平台公開表達訴求，但佔領運動始終有其缺點，一味據守陣地會虛耗資源和精力，民氣隨時間消耗，又更容易成為鎮壓目標。<br />\n<br />\n黃背心示威者反其道而行，不死守任何公共空間，在每個星期六湧上街頭，沒有任何既定路線，不預先公佈時間下快閃式堵路，用各種直接行動撼動政權。譬如堵塞高速公路和迴旋處，接管或燒毀道路收費站，讓汽車自由通行，令政府無利可圖。"}]}